Config command now resets the state of Class Manager and prevents users from using the undo command to reach a state before Class Manager was configured.
Config command now only allows for tutorial and assignment counts to be between 1 to 40 inclusive. This fixes division by zero errors for class details data visualiation,
as well as prevents the app from freezing or crashing when the count is too large.
